      "label": "Kellan Or",
      "preview": "# Kellan Or\n\nKellan Or is a cistern scout who sells route rumors to anyone willing to cross the [[Old Roads]].\n\nHe once carried the [[Glass Key]] for the [[Ashen Choir]], but he claims the key changed hands before [[Mara Voss]] arrived at [[Ash Gate]].\n\n## Playable Pressure\n\n- Kellan can become an ally if Mara shares the truth of the [[Iron Meridian]].\n- He withholds cistern access unless the player has the [[Cinder Lantern]] or a favor from the [[Glass Cartographers]].",
